gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Watered milk in a vessel, burnt offerings to the god; 
Various tongues cry out, it is lost in renunciation itself.

Here is the translation:

Panch indriyunu poshna svad, pandy poshtata vade pramad; 
Pachi purushottama na bhajay, tena khotya chhe vairegy may.

Oil of champa flowers, oil of champak; 
That which is not willing to leave it within itself, 
To whom renunciation takes place in the mind.

Here is the translation:

This has won which tastes the self, then all calamities are averted; 
Won taste becomes pure by itself, with natural joy and great power.
